>\n得番d大路連鎖同車站商店有野食<br />\n<br />\n如果可以不如聖誕去好過<br />\n大陸同日本都唔係假期<br />\n雖然我都未試過"},{"pid":"10c758aa2e85b6bafa2146a439baf762c3cd2d54","tid":522264,"uid":43082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T16:26:11.000Z","msg":"好多食肆唔開架"},{"pid":"d46681a268a5af22612e31541dadded5844318d4","tid":522264,"uid":92462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T16:36:09.000Z","msg":"我一丁友去hea食應該無咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連鎖店/毒撚食店開就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到時睇機票住宿價錢再決定,主要想試一次日本倒數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 福袋買唔買都係其次"}]}